[ ] Screenshots — minimum 5 required
    - Recommended: Home tab, Draft board, Playoff bracket, Franchise tab,
      Commissioner mode (Team Editor or Player Editor)

[ ] Trailer Video — strongly recommended, not required
    - 30–90 seconds showing core gameplay loop

[ ] Store Description
    - Short description (up to 300 characters)
    - Long description (full HTML-friendly detail page)
    - Tags: Turn-Based Strategy, Sports, Management, Simulation

[ ] Age Rating — IARC questionnaire (in Steamworks dashboard)
    - Gridiron Dynasty will likely rate E or E10+ (no violence, no explicit
      content) which has no restrictions on storefront visibility

[ ] Privacy Policy URL
    - Steam requires a privacy policy link even for single-player offline apps
    - A simple one-page hosted policy (GitHub Pages or similar) is sufficient
    - State that no personal data is collected, all saves are stored locally

[ ] System Requirements (fill in Steamworks)
    - Minimum: Windows 10 64-bit, 4GB RAM, 200MB disk
    - Recommended: Windows 10/11 64-bit, 8GB RAM, SSD

